## Phase 10 Readiness

Phase 10 (Pipeline Save/Load) will need:
1. **File save/open dialogs** — `tauri-plugin-dialog` already in [package.json](file:///Users/adev/playground/CrossQL/package.json) but missing from Rust side
2. **Pipeline serialization** — TypeScript types in [types.ts](file:///Users/adev/playground/CrossQL/src/lib/types.ts) exist; canvas state (nodes + edges + configs) already flows as JSON
3. **Recent files list** — Will need a small local storage mechanism (Tauri store plugin or a simple JSON file)

> [!TIP]
> Before starting Phase 10, strongly consider refactoring [+page.svelte](file:///Users/adev/playground/CrossQL/src/routes/+page.svelte) into focused modules. The current monolith will make save/load, undo/redo, and keyboard shortcuts (Phase 12) significantly harder to implement cleanly.
